<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.4">
<l>kaṉṉaṟku ṭantiṟantā lottūṟik kaṇakaṇa cirittuvantu</l>
<l>muṉvantu niṉṟumut tantarumeṉ mukilvaṇṇaṉ tirumārvaṉ</l>
<l>taṉṉaippeṟṟēṟ kuttaṉvā yamutamtan teṉṉaittaḷirp pikkiṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>taṉṉeṟṟu māṟṟalarta laikaḷmītē taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having come laughing ‘ha ha ha’ [with nectar] flowing</l>
<l>like a pot of sugar cane [juice] when opened,</l>
<l>my cloud-hued one with Śrī on his chest</l>
<l>who comes and stands before [me] giving [me] a kiss,</l>
<l>having given the nectar of his mouth to me who begot him,</l>
<l>he causes me to rejoice.</l>
<l>Will he not come with a tottering walk on top of the heads of the enemies who strike him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
